product1.title: Sharpy
product1.description: Sharpy is a 189W moving beam light with an unprecedented brightness usually achievable only with far greater wattages. Sharpy is also groundbreaking for the purity of its beam, which is determined defined and free of any halo or discoloration around the edges.
